Step 1: Install header files by typing following command:

	sudo apt-get install linux-headers-$(uname -r)


Step 2: Compile the Kernel Module
	
	Run 'make' command (in the directory containing makefile and your-module.c file)


Step 3: Insert Module 
	
	Run sudo insmod ./module_name.ko 
		
		OR
 
	Run sudo insmod ./module_name.ko var_name = var_value ..


Step 4: To see output

	Run dmesg|tail -6
